{"number":19,"verseCount":41,"verses":[[1,["I am ",["Alpha and Omega",["study-note-ref","a",[["Rev. 1:8 (8, 11)","nt/rev/1.8"],"; ",["D&C 35:1","dc-testament/dc/35.1"],"; ",["45:7","dc-testament/dc/45.7"],"; ",["54:1","dc-testament/dc/54.1"],"; ",["61:1","dc-testament/dc/61.1"],"; ",["68:35","dc-testament/dc/68.35"],"; ",["75:1","dc-testament/dc/75.1"],"."]]],", ",["Christ",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Messiah","tg/jesus-christ-messiah"],"."]]]," the Lord; yea, even I am he, the beginning and the end, the Redeemer of the ",["world",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG World","tg/world"],"."]]],"."]],[2,["I, having accomplished and ",["finished",["study-note-ref","a",[["John 17:4","nt/john/17.4"],"; ",["3 Ne. 11:11","bofm/3-ne/11.11"],"."]]]," the will of him whose I am, even the Father, concerning me—having done this that I might ",["subdue",["study-note-ref","b",[["Philip. 3:21","nt/philip/3.21"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Mission of","tg/jesus-christ-mission-of"],"."]]]," all things unto myself—"]],[3,["Retaining all ",["power",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Power of","tg/jesus-christ-power-of"],"."]]],", even to the ",["destroying",["study-note-ref","b",[["Gen. 3:15","ot/gen/3.15"],"; ",["Rom. 16:20","nt/rom/16.20"],"; ",["1 Jn. 3:8","nt/1-jn/3.8"],"; ",["Rev. 20:10 (8, 10)","nt/rev/20.10"],"; ",["D&C 29:28 (27–30, 44)","dc-testament/dc/29.28"],"; ",["88:114 (111–15)","dc-testament/dc/88.114"],"."]]]," of Satan and his works at the ",["end",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG World, End of","tg/world-end-of"],"."]]]," of the world, and the last great day of judgment, which I shall pass upon the inhabitants thereof, ",["judging",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Jesus Christ, Judge","tg/jesus-christ-judge"],"; ",["Judgment, the Last","tg/judgment-the-last"],"; ",["Justice","tg/justice"],"."]]]," every man according to his ",["works",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Good Works","tg/good-works"],"."]]]," and the deeds which he hath done."]],[4,["And surely every man must ",["repent",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Repent","tg/repent"],"."]]]," or ",["suffer",["study-note-ref","b",[["Luke 13:3","nt/luke/13.3"],"."]]],", for I, God, am ",["endless",["study-note-ref","c",[["Moses 1:3","pgp/moses/1.3"],"."]]],"."]],[5,["Wherefore, I ",["revoke",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 56:4","dc-testament/dc/56.4"],"; ",["58:32","dc-testament/dc/58.32"],"."]]]," not the judgments which I shall pass, but woes shall go forth, weeping, ",["wailing",["study-note-ref","b",[["Matt. 13:42","nt/matt/13.42"],"."]]]," and gnashing of teeth, yea, to those who are found on my ",["left",["study-note-ref","c",[["Matt. 25:41","nt/matt/25.41"],"."]]]," hand."]],[6,["Nevertheless, it is ",["not",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 76:106 (105–6)","dc-testament/dc/76.106"],"; ",["138:59","dc-testament/dc/138.59"],"."]]]," written that there shall be no end to this torment, but it is written ",[["endless",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 76:44 (33, 44–45)","dc-testament/dc/76.44"],"."]]]," ",["torment",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Punish","tg/punish"],"."]]],".",[""]]]],[7,["Again, it is written ",[["eternal damnation",["study-note-ref","a",[["Hel. 12:26 (25–26)","bofm/hel/12.26"],"; ",["D&C 29:44","dc-testament/dc/29.44"],"."]]],";",[""]]," wherefore it is more express than other scriptures, that it might work upon the hearts of the children of men, altogether for my name’s glory."]],[8,["Wherefore, I will explain unto ",["",32],"you this ",["mystery",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 13:11","nt/matt/13.11"],"."]]],", for it is meet unto you to know even as mine apostles."]],[9,["I speak unto you that are chosen in this thing, even as one, that you may enter into my ",["rest",["study-note-ref","a",[["Heb. 4:3 (3, 5)","nt/heb/4.3"],"; ",["2 Ne. 21:10","bofm/2-ne/21.10"],"."]]],"."]],[10,["For, behold, the ",["mystery",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Tim. 3:16","nt/1-tim/3.16"],"; ",["Jacob 4:8","bofm/jacob/4.8"],"; ",["D&C 76:114 (114–16)","dc-testament/dc/76.114"],"."]]]," of godliness, how great is it! For, behold, I am ",["endless",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG God, Eternal Nature of","tg/god-eternal-nature-of"],"."]]],", and the punishment which is given from my hand is endless ",["punishment",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Punish","tg/punish"],"."]]],", for ",["Endless",["study-note-ref","d",[["Ex. 3:15","ot/ex/3.15"],"; ",["Moses 1:3","pgp/moses/1.3"],"; ",["7:35","pgp/moses/7.35"],"."]]]," is my name. Wherefore—"]],[11,[["Eternal",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 25:46","nt/matt/25.46"],". ",["TG Punish","tg/punish"],"."]]]," punishment is God’s punishment."]],[12,["Endless punishment is God’s punishment."]],[13,["Wherefore, I command you to repent, and keep the ",["commandments",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 5:2 (1–18)","dc-testament/dc/5.2"],"; ",["10:6 (6–7)","dc-testament/dc/10.6"],"; ",["17:8 (1–9)","dc-testament/dc/17.8"],"."]]]," which you have received by the hand of my servant Joseph Smith, Jun., in my name;"]],[14,["And it is by my almighty power that you have received them;"]],[15,["Therefore I command you to repent—repent, lest I ",["smite",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ps. 2:9","ot/ps/2.9"],"; ",["Isa. 11:4 (1–4)","ot/isa/11.4"],"."]]]," you by the rod of my mouth, and by my wrath, and by my anger, and your ",["sufferings",["study-note-ref","b",[["Alma 36:12 (11–19)","bofm/alma/36.12"],"."]]]," be sore—how sore you know not, how exquisite you know not, yea, how hard to bear you know not."]],[16,["For behold, I, God, have ",["suffered",["study-note-ref","a",[["2 Cor. 5:14","nt/2-cor/5.14"],"; ",["Alma 11:40 (40–41)","bofm/alma/11.40"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through","tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Redeemer","tg/jesus-christ-redeemer"],"; ",["Redemption","tg/redemption"],"."]]]," these things for all, that they ",["might",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Mercy","tg/mercy"],"."]]]," not suffer if they would ",["repent",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Remission of Sins","tg/remission-of-sins"],"."]]],";"]],[17,["But if they would not repent they must ",["suffer",["study-note-ref","a",[["Mark 14:36","nt/mark/14.36"],"; ",["Alma 11:40 (40–41)","bofm/alma/11.40"],"; ",["D&C 29:17","dc-testament/dc/29.17"],"."]]]," even as I;"]],[18,["Which ",["suffering",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Pain","tg/pain"],"; ",["Suffering","tg/suffering"],"."]]]," caused myself, even God, the greatest of all, to tremble because of pain, and to bleed at every pore, and to suffer both body and spirit—and would that I might ",["not",["study-note-ref","b",[["Luke 22:42 (42–44)","nt/luke/22.42"],"."]]]," drink the bitter cup, and shrink—"]],[19,["Nevertheless, glory be to the Father, and I partook and ",["finished",["study-note-ref","a",[["John 17:4","nt/john/17.4"],"; ",["19:30","nt/john/19.30"],"; ",["Heb. 12:2 (1–3)","nt/heb/12.2"],"."]]]," my preparations unto the children of men."]],[20,["Wherefore, I command you again to repent, lest I ",["humble",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG God, Indignation of","tg/god-indignation-of"],"."]]]," you with my almighty power; and that you ",["confess",["study-note-ref","b",[["Num. 5:7 (6–10)","ot/num/5.7"],"; ",["D&C 58:43","dc-testament/dc/58.43"],"; ",["64:7","dc-testament/dc/64.7"],". ",["TG Confession","tg/confession"],"."]]]," your sins, lest you suffer these ",["punishments",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Despair","tg/despair"],"; ",["Punish","tg/punish"],"."]]]," of which I have spoken, of which in the smallest, yea, even in the least degree you have ",["tasted",["study-note-ref","d",[["D&C 10:7 (1–7)","dc-testament/dc/10.7"],". ",["TG Holy Ghost, Loss of","tg/holy-ghost-loss-of"],"."]]]," at the time I withdrew my Spirit."]],[21,["And I command you that you ",["preach",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 11:9","dc-testament/dc/11.9"],"."]]]," naught but repentance, and show ",["not",["study-note-ref","b",[["Moses 1:42","pgp/moses/1.42"],"; ",["4:32","pgp/moses/4.32"],"; ",["JS—H 1:42","pgp/js-h/1.42"],"."]]]," these things unto the world until it is wisdom in me."]],[22,["For they cannot ",["bear",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 78:18 (17–18)","dc-testament/dc/78.18"],"."]]]," meat now, but ",["milk",["study-note-ref","b",[["Isa. 28:9","ot/isa/28.9"],"; ",["1 Cor. 3:2 (2–3)","nt/1-cor/3.2"],"; ",["Heb. 5:12 (11–14)","nt/heb/5.12"],"; ",["D&C 50:40","dc-testament/dc/50.40"],"."]]]," they must receive; wherefore, they must not know these things, lest they perish."]],[23,[["Learn",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Education","tg/education"],"; ",["Learn","tg/learn"],"."]]]," of me, and listen to my words; ",["walk",["study-note-ref","b",[["1 Jn. 2:6","nt/1-jn/2.6"],"; ",["Moro. 7:4 (3–4)","bofm/moro/7.4"],"."]]]," in the ",["meekness",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Meek","tg/meek"],"."]]]," of my Spirit, and you shall have ",["peace",["study-note-ref","d",[["Micah 5:5","ot/micah/5.5"],". ",["TG Peace of God","tg/peace-of-god"],"."]]]," in me."]],[24,["I am Jesus Christ; I ",["came",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Birth of","tg/jesus-christ-birth-of"],"."]]]," by the ",["will",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG God, Will of","tg/god-will-of"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Authority of","tg/jesus-christ-authority-of"],"."]]]," of the Father, and I do his will."]],[25,["And again, I command thee that thou shalt not ",["covet",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Covet","tg/covet"],"."]]]," thy ",["",33],["neighbor’s",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Neighbor","tg/neighbor"],"."]]]," ",["wife",["study-note-ref","c",[["Ex. 20:17","ot/ex/20.17"],"; ",["1 Cor. 7:2 (2–4)","nt/1-cor/7.2"],". ",["TG Adulterer","tg/adulterer"],"; ",["Lust","tg/lust"],"; ",["Marriage, Husbands","tg/marriage-husbands"],"; ",["Marriage, Wives","tg/marriage-wives"],"."]]],"; nor seek thy neighbor’s life."]],[26,["And again, I command thee that thou shalt not ",["covet",["study-note-ref","a",[["Acts 5:1 (1–11)","nt/acts/5.1"],"."]]]," thine own property, but impart it freely to the printing of the Book of Mormon, which contains the ",["truth",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Truth","tg/truth"],"."]]]," and the word of God—"]],[27,["Which is my word to the ",["Gentile",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Ne. 13:42","bofm/1-ne/13.42"],"; ",["3 Ne. 16:7 (4–13)","bofm/3-ne/16.7"],"; ",["D&C 18:6 (6, 26)","dc-testament/dc/18.6"],"; ",["21:12","dc-testament/dc/21.12"],"; ",["90:9 (8–9)","dc-testament/dc/90.9"],"; ",["107:33","dc-testament/dc/107.33"],"; ",["112:4","dc-testament/dc/112.4"],"."]]],", that soon it may go to the ",["Jew",["study-note-ref","b",[["2 Ne. 26:12","bofm/2-ne/26.12"],"; ",["30:7 (7–8)","bofm/2-ne/30.7"],"; ",["Morm. 5:14 (12–14)","bofm/morm/5.14"],"."]]],", of whom the Lamanites are a ",["remnant",["study-note-ref","c",[["Omni 1:15 (14–19)","bofm/omni/1.15"],"; ",["Mosiah 25:2 (2–4)","bofm/mosiah/25.2"],"; ",["Hel. 8:21","bofm/hel/8.21"],"; ",["D&C 52:2","dc-testament/dc/52.2"],"; ",["109:65","dc-testament/dc/109.65"],"."]]],", that they may believe the gospel, and look not for a ",["Messiah",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Jesus Christ, Messiah","tg/jesus-christ-messiah"],"."]]]," to come who has already come."]],[28,["And again, I command thee that thou shalt ",["pray",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Tim. 2:8","nt/1-tim/2.8"],". ",["TG Prayer","tg/prayer"],"."]]]," ",["vocally",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 20:47 (47, 51)","dc-testament/dc/20.47"],"; ",["23:6","dc-testament/dc/23.6"],"."]]]," as well as in thy heart; yea, before the world as well as in secret, in public as well as in private."]],[29,["And thou shalt ",["declare",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Preaching","tg/preaching"],"."]]]," glad tidings, yea, ",["publish",["study-note-ref","b",[["Mark 13:10","nt/mark/13.10"],"."]]]," it upon the mountains, and upon every high place, and among every people that thou shalt be permitted to see."]],[30,["And thou shalt do it with all humility, ",["trusting",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Trust in God","tg/trust-in-god"],"."]]]," in me, ",["reviling",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Forbear","tg/forbear"],"; ",["Retribution","tg/retribution"],"; ",["Reviling","tg/reviling"],"; ",["Strife","tg/strife"],"."]]]," not against revilers."]],[31,["And of ",["tenets",["study-note-ref","a",[["2 Tim. 2:23 (23–24)","nt/2-tim/2.23"],"."]]]," thou shalt not talk, but thou shalt declare repentance and ",["faith",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Baptism, Qualifications for","tg/baptism-qualifications-for"],"; ",["Faith","tg/faith"],"."]]]," on the Savior, and ",["remission",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Remission of Sins","tg/remission-of-sins"],"."]]]," of sins by ",["baptism",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Baptism","tg/baptism"],"."]]],", and by ",["fire",["study-note-ref","e",[["Matt. 3:11","nt/matt/3.11"],"."]]],", yea, even the ",["Holy Ghost",["study-note-ref","f",[["TG Holy Ghost, Baptism of","tg/holy-ghost-baptism-of"],"."]]],"."]],[32,["Behold, this is a great and the last ",["commandment",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 58:26 (26–29)","dc-testament/dc/58.26"],"."]]]," which I shall give unto you concerning this matter; for this shall suffice for thy daily walk, even unto the end of thy life."]],[33,["And misery thou shalt receive if thou wilt slight these ",["counsels",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Counsel","tg/counsel"],"."]]],", yea, even the destruction of thyself and property."]],[34,[["Impart",["study-note-ref","a",[["Acts 4:37 (34–37)","nt/acts/4.37"],"."]]]," a portion of thy property, yea, even part of thy lands, and all save the support of thy ",["family",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Family","tg/family"],"."]]],"."]],[35,["Pay the ",["debt",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Debt","tg/debt"],"."]]]," thou hast ",["contracted",["study-note-ref","b",["IE to pay for the publication of the first edition of the Book of Mormon."]]]," with the printer. Release thyself from ",["bondage",["study-note-ref","c",[["Prov. 22:7","ot/prov/22.7"],". ",["TG Bondage, Physical","tg/bondage-physical"],"."]]],"."]],[36,[["Leave",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 19:29","nt/matt/19.29"],"."]]]," thy house and home, except when thou shalt desire to see thy family;"]],[37,["And ",["speak",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ps. 105:2","ot/ps/105.2"],"; ",["Heb. 13:16","nt/heb/13.16"],"; ",["D&C 58:47","dc-testament/dc/58.47"],"; ",["63:37","dc-testament/dc/63.37"],"; ",["68:8","dc-testament/dc/68.8"],"; ",["71:7","dc-testament/dc/71.7"],"."]]]," freely to all; yea, preach, exhort, declare the ",["truth",["study-note-ref","b",[["2 Cor. 4:2","nt/2-cor/4.2"],"; ",["D&C 75:4","dc-testament/dc/75.4"],"."]]],", even with a loud voice, with a sound of rejoicing, crying—Hosanna, hosanna, blessed be the name of the Lord God!"]],[38,[["Pray",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Prayer","tg/prayer"],"."]]]," always, and I will ",["pour out",["study-note-ref","b",[["Prov. 1:23","ot/prov/1.23"],"; ",["Acts 2:17","nt/acts/2.17"],"; ",["D&C 95:4","dc-testament/dc/95.4"],"."]]]," my Spirit upon you, and great shall be your blessing—yea, even more than if you should obtain ",["treasures",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Treasure","tg/treasure"],"."]]]," of earth and corruptibleness to the extent thereof."]],[39,["Behold, canst thou read this without ",["rejoicing",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Joy","tg/joy"],"."]]]," and lifting up thy heart for ",["gladness",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Cheerful","tg/cheerful"],"."]]],"?"]],[40,["Or canst thou run about longer as a ",["blind",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 23:16 (16, 24)","nt/matt/23.16"],"."]]]," guide?"]],[41,["Or canst thou be ",["humble",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Humility","tg/humility"],"; ",["Meek","tg/meek"],"."]]]," and meek, and conduct thyself wisely before me? Yea, ",["come",["study-note-ref","b",[["Matt. 11:28 (28–30)","nt/matt/11.28"],"."]]]," unto me thy Savior. Amen."]]],"volume":"dc"}